Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:00.74,0:00:04.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,☆Dragon Ball Super☆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:10.61,0:00:14.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,曾经淡忘的梦想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:14.84,0:00:19.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,如今再续前缘　又开始燃亮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:20.52,0:00:24.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,给星星都连上线
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:24.85,0:00:28.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就这样给宇宙画出了门框
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:30.44,0:00:34.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,跻身于全新的舞台上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:35.45,0:00:40.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,向诸神发出挑战
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:40.62,0:00:42.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,强烈☆猛烈☆活力满泻！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:42.66,0:00:45.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Let's Go！Go！恐慌奔走！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:45.17,0:00:49.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你输了就能变更强
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:49.88,0:00:55.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不知天高地厚又何妨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:55.55,0:01:00.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,生无可悔　身无界限　一往无前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:00.51,0:01:02.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,壮烈☆激烈☆活力爆裂！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:02.64,0:01:05.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Let's Go！Yes！拳脚不绝！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:05.14,0:01:09.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,去沐浴颤抖的感觉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:09.90,0:01:13.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一个壮大传说　正在等着你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:27.43,0:01:30.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,出现在地球战士面前的塔格玛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:30.14,0:01:32.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,拥有压倒性的力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:33.10,0:01:35.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,而把塔格玛身体夺走的是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:36.48,0:01:41.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我是基纽特战队队长，基纽！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:42.40,0:01:46.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,其中，由于长时间远离战斗的悟饭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:46.82,0:01:51.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,再次变身为超级赛亚人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:51.87,0:01:54.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,局势似乎有所逆转
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:54.79,0:01:57.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,却没料到弗利萨突然插手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:57.54,0:02:02.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,悟饭陷入了绝境
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:02.80,0:02:04.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,死吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:07.22,0:02:10.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,比…比克叔叔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:13.68,0:02:20.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,「地球！悟饭！命悬一线！快来啊孙悟空！！」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:39.67,0:02:41.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你在做什么啊，比克
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:41.42,0:02:43.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,快点站起来啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:43.21,0:02:47.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,妈妈…已经感觉不了比克叔叔的气了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:47.26,0:02:48.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:48.30,0:02:49.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,唔…嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:55.27,0:02:56.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,比克叔叔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.40,0:03:10.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,比克叔叔！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:11.53,0:03:16.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真棒，这充满绝望的叫声
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:16.96,0:03:20.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这才是我一直追求的东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.84,0:03:24.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,来吧，再让我愉快一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.46,0:03:27.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,都是因为我，比克叔叔才会死的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.51,0:03:28.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,悟饭！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.20,0:03:28.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,站住
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.59,0:03:32.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,骗人的吧…比克死了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.26,0:03:33.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,所以我才说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.68,0:03:36.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那些家伙不好惹，会出人命的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.52,0:03:39.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,回去以后，我要撤下地球的工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:40.10,0:03:40.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你怎么这样！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.31,0:03:42.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,要，要打架吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.32,0:03:50.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真是的，孙君和贝吉塔到底在做什么啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.66,0:03:51.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.82,0:03:52.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.63,0:04:04.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,太好吃了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.46,0:04:07.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,披萨真好吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.30,0:04:11.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这个拉得长长的乳酪实在太棒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.80,0:04:14.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,味道也有点特别
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.64,0:04:17.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,维斯，再来一份
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.50,0:04:19.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那已经是最后一份了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.77,0:04:20.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.27,0:04:27.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我猜比鲁斯大人您会喜欢披萨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.65,0:04:30.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,所以从布玛小姐那拿了很多
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.45,0:04:34.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,剩下的要用我的手杖才能拿出来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.16,0:04:36.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那拿出来啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.79,0:04:42.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是比鲁斯大人让我把
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.15,0:04:45.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,孙悟空先生和贝吉塔先生扔在那里面的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.42,0:04:48.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就是说手杖在使用中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.97,0:04:57.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你不会是忘记了吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.97,0:05:00.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我才没忘！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.06,0:05:05.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不过，最重要的事情还是我的食物！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.36,0:05:07.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,来！快给我披萨！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.11,0:05:08.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.07,0:05:16.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,痛…你干什么啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.41,0:05:20.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,刚好练得起劲呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.62,0:05:24.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,哼！你们修炼得
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.21,0:05:26.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,挺充实嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:30.42,0:05:31.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,把你们变干净了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.97,0:05:33.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,喂！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.63,0:05:34.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,来了来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.10,0:05:42.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,哎呀？全空了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.64,0:05:44.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真是多亏了这些慰劳品啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:44.98,0:05:47.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,食物居然从手杖里出来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.31,0:05:50.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,还以为我们会饿死呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.07,0:05:55.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你们…不会是把我的披萨全部都…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.70,0:05:59.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不可原谅！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.24,0:05:59.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,糟糕，快逃！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.20,0:06:03.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,居然全都吃了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.16,0:06:05.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你们什么意思！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.79,0:06:07.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没办法啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.25,0:06:11.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,明明是你这家伙把我们扔去那种地方！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.09,0:06:14.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什么这家伙！居然这么和破坏神说话！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.88,0:06:18.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,看来，又要再去拿一些披萨回来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.64,0:06:22.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,咦，这是…信息？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.39,0:06:23.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不快点的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.48,0:06:26.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这个豪华草莓芭菲就融化掉了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:26.65,0:06:29.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,豪华草莓芭菲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.15,0:06:33.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,哎呀，颜色这么炫，看上去很好吃啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.15,0:06:34.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.11,0:06:34.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嗯…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.03,0:06:38.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,味道如何呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.49,0:06:42.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但是，看上去慌慌张张的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.25,0:06:45.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,联系一下吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.41,0:06:46.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,布玛小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.38,0:06:50.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎…怎么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.13,0:06:53.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你怎么现在才回复啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.76,0:06:56.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,妈妈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.30,0:06:59.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,芭菲什么的先别管了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.26,0:07:02.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,帮忙叫贝吉塔和孙君快点回来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.27,0:07:07.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,她到底在和谁说话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.19,0:07:08.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,给我听好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.65,0:07:12.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那个超恶劣的混蛋弗利萨复活了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.23,0:07:15.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,现在地球有危险！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.74,0:07:17.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,说我混蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.53,0:07:20.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,弗利萨大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:20.03,0:07:22.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,要不我去杀了那女人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.53,0:07:23.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,稍等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.24,0:07:27.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,看来她已经联络上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.29,0:07:29.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那个家伙了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.79,0:07:30.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,弗利萨？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.17,0:07:36.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是那个弗利萨吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.47,0:07:39.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎么回事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.97,0:07:43.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不仅如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.31,0:07:45.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他变得非常强大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.60,0:07:48.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,为了保护悟饭，比克他还被杀了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.10,0:07:49.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,比克吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.15,0:07:51.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,知道了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.27,0:07:53.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,现在就让维斯先生带我们回去！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.94,0:07:57.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,去地球的话需要35分钟呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.86,0:07:59.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不会吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.36,0:08:00.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我记得
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.99,0:08:03.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你好像会瞬间移动的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.62,0:08:04.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可是，那个…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.20,0:08:06.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,卡卡罗特
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:09.42,0:08:10.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,果然，还是不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.96,0:08:13.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,离地球太远了，谁的气都感觉不到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.13,0:08:16.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,现在是说这些的时候吗！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.09,0:08:19.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,再集中精神去找啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.05,0:08:25.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,情况这么危急，还要等35分钟？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.73,0:08:33.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,看来孙悟空是不能马上来这里了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.77,0:08:37.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那么，弗利萨大人，先让我收拾他们吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:38.24,0:08:42.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可以，等孙悟空来到地球时
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:42.82,0:08:46.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,如果，你们大家全死光了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.99,0:08:50.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那会是多么愉快啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.38,0:09:05.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我…突然有紧急任务
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.97,0:09:07.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就先失陪了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.60,0:09:09.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我们…要完蛋了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:09.60,0:09:10.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,喂…喂！放开我！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.15,0:09:13.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,等下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.36,0:09:19.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,由于长期远离战斗，把道服也弄丢的我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.19,0:09:22.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,根本就没有力量去保护大家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.20,0:09:26.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,喂喂，你那千疮百孔的身体
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.20,0:09:27.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,还站起来干嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.37,0:09:31.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,如果我像爸爸一样持续修炼的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:32.04,0:09:35.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,比克叔叔就不会死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:35.54,0:09:39.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,都死到临头还抱怨什么，真没种
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.63,0:09:41.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你没有错！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.59,0:09:43.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,为了家人而远离战斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:43.88,0:09:45.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这是理所当然的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.77,0:09:52.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,请放心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.89,0:09:55.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你那些重要的家人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.77,0:10:01.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我会在一瞬间，把他们杀掉的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.69,0:10:05.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我为了保护家人和大家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.99,0:10:08.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,必须在这里阻止你！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:17.79,0:10:19.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,居然还有这种力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:20.17,0:10:23.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,等一下悟饭！坚持…等悟空回来！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.97,0:10:29.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真是胡闹呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:29.22,0:10:30.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,身体能顶得住吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.97,0:10:31.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:31.85,0:10:32.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,卡卡罗特！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.61,0:10:41.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,悟饭哥哥…你会死的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:41.90,0:10:43.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,哥哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:43.53,0:10:45.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,悟饭，不要操之过急！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.49,0:10:49.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,悟饭！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:51.83,0:10:55.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,看吧看吧，身体要坏掉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:11.43,0:11:12.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,抓住我，贝吉塔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.18,0:11:17.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,别磨磨蹭蹭的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:18.85,0:11:20.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,先走了，比鲁斯大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.66,0:11:35.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,总算放弃了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.75,0:11:39.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那么，该是时候永别了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:00.15,0:12:03.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,总算和你见面了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:04.11,0:12:06.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,孙悟空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.09,0:12:31.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,贝吉塔，还有孙君
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:31.68,0:12:32.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:32.80,0:12:34.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他们终于回来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:34.64,0:12:35.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.64,0:12:39.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,喂，贝吉塔！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.04,0:12:42.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你打算把我这个美人妻子丢开到什么时候啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.27,0:12:46.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你丈夫长了一张坏人脸呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:46.11,0:12:47.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你说什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:49.19,0:12:53.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,悟空…原来悟饭是为了这个才耗尽力气的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.87,0:12:58.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那个人就是以前打倒弗利萨大人的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.85,0:13:00.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,赛亚人吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.33,0:13:04.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没错，我是绝对不会忘记
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.84,0:13:08.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,孙悟空的那张讨厌的脸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.42,0:13:11.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真是抱歉，悟饭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.22,0:13:13.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你的气我感受到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.80,0:13:15.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,做得好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:15.39,0:13:16.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:16.60,0:13:19.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我把爸爸叫过来已经使尽全力了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.73,0:13:24.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,而且… 比克叔叔还为了我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.15,0:13:26.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没关系的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.80,0:13:28.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,比克他，可以用那美克星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:28.94,0:13:30.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,的龙珠复活
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:31.70,0:13:32.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.66,0:13:38.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,比克，我一定会让你复活的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.58,0:13:41.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.25,0:13:44.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那是亚德拉特星人的瞬间移动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:45.42,0:13:47.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,该不会是逃走了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:47.71,0:13:49.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,看，又回来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:53.30,0:13:55.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,赛亚人居然学了这麻烦的招式
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:55.97,0:13:58.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那么我去把士兵叫过来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:00.02,0:14:03.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,刚好，趁此机会可以试试我的力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:06.19,0:14:07.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,悟天！特兰克斯！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.57,0:14:10.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我把比克的身体交给丹迪来保管了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.23,0:14:13.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你们去和他说明一下情况！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.53,0:14:14.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:19.41,0:14:22.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但是，接下来爸爸你会打倒弗利萨的吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.70,0:14:24.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,让我们也看看嘛！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:24.96,0:14:26.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,别任性了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.75,0:14:29.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,接下来不是小孩子该呆的地方！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.75,0:14:31.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,唔…嗯…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:32.09,0:14:33.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可是啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:33.55,0:14:36.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,特兰克斯！听他的话！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:37.09,0:14:40.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,爸爸！我…我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.77,0:14:44.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好！那么我就负责
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.52,0:14:45.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,把你们带到安全的地方！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.39,0:14:47.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你给我留下来！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.02,0:14:50.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,比起弗利萨，我更怕布玛啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.07,0:14:53.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一定要打倒弗利萨！我们说好了喔！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.99,0:14:58.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,悟饭，吃仙豆吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:02.12,0:15:03.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,谢谢你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:04.50,0:15:06.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你们没问题吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:06.50,0:15:08.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我们没事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:08.54,0:15:11.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,而且，总得留下一颗以防万一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:11.67,0:15:12.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,非常抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.00,0:15:15.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,再说，我们恢复了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:15.59,0:15:17.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,也帮不了什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:19.22,0:15:23.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真是的，悟空总是在这种时候出现
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.85,0:15:27.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,接下来，只能相信悟空他们了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:35.40,0:15:38.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,孙悟空先生，我等你很久了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:39.53,0:15:42.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,终于可以向你复仇了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.29,0:15:45.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不过，贝吉塔先生居然会和你在一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:45.62,0:15:47.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这倒是让我有点意外
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:47.50,0:15:48.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,哼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.71,0:15:51.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,看来真的是弗利萨呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.38,0:15:54.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你到底是怎么复活的？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.01,0:15:57.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他用了龙珠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:57.63,0:15:58.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没错吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.93,0:16:00.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没错！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:00.76,0:16:02.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我终于回来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:03.47,0:16:06.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,终于离开了那个可恨的地狱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:06.68,0:16:08.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我在地狱里像结草虫似的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.52,0:16:12.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,被吊在一片花田中，一直不能动弹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:13.61,0:16:16.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,每天被迫在看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:16.03,0:16:19.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,跳舞和游行表演
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:19.61,0:16:23.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你知道那是多么痛苦的事吗！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:23.20,0:16:24.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我才不知道呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:25.12,0:16:27.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是你自己擅自跑来地球
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.54,0:16:30.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,才会被特兰克斯杀掉吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:31.04,0:16:35.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,所有的起因都是因为你，孙悟空先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.75,0:16:39.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,对我来说，有你活在这世上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:39.09,0:16:42.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,简直让我气不打一处来！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:42.89,0:16:46.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这种心情，我基纽能感同身受
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:46.81,0:16:48.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,基纽？是那个…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:48.73,0:16:51.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在那美克星，偷我身体的人吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:51.98,0:16:53.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真的是基纽？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:53.48,0:16:56.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你在那时候不是变成青蛙了吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:56.23,0:16:59.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你们能明白从那之后我的感受吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:00.03,0:17:03.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,变什么不好，偏偏是青蛙！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:04.62,0:17:07.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你们知道我有多么悲惨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.33,0:17:09.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,多么痛苦吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:09.12,0:17:11.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真是遗憾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:13.12,0:17:14.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什…什么！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:15.54,0:17:16.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,继续做青蛙的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:16.92,0:17:19.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你至少不会死呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:20.34,0:17:21.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,等下！贝吉塔！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:31.10,0:17:32.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,基…基纽队长！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:33.02,0:17:36.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,贝吉塔，你也不用杀了他啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:36.31,0:17:39.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,哼！我只是消灭了会妨碍战斗的家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:41.70,0:17:43.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,贝吉塔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:43.15,0:17:46.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你好像厉害多了嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:46.28,0:17:47.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,别着急
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:47.78,0:17:51.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,等我杀死悟空先生后，就轮到你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:51.16,0:17:55.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,哼，我会在卡卡罗特出手之前就干掉你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:08.43,0:18:10.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这样子看来，弗利萨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:10.35,0:18:12.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你比以前强了不少嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:12.68,0:18:14.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,说得没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:14.60,0:18:18.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我复活后，为了今天这场战斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:18.20,0:18:20.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可是拼命在训练呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:20.61,0:18:23.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这可是我第一次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:23.53,0:18:25.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这么努力呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:26.36,0:18:30.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,托你的福，我获得了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:30.08,0:18:32.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,超乎想象的力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:34.96,0:18:37.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,或许，你是变强了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.00,0:18:41.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但是，你不觉得我们也变强了吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:41.96,0:18:44.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,看来，我有必要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:44.17,0:18:46.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,让你们瞧瞧我的力量才行呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:47.26,0:18:51.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,之前我确实是大意了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:51.60,0:18:54.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这次就一口气变成最终形态吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:10.99,0:19:12.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,弗利萨大人，难道…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:15.79,0:19:18.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,糟了！大家，快逃！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:35.02,0:19:36.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,弗利萨大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:37.10,0:19:40.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎么回事，所有士兵都…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:41.40,0:19:44.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那家伙，把伙伴都消灭了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:04.05,0:20:07.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,为了展示自己的力量，不惜把士兵都杀了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:10.43,0:20:12.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,让你们久等了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:13.26,0:20:17.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好了，复仇的准备已经就绪了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:20.27,0:20:22.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这太厉害了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:23.73,0:20:26.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你到底做了怎样的训练？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:28.99,0:20:30.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,喂，贝吉塔！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:31.07,0:20:33.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,抱歉了，让我去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:34.03,0:20:35.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你说什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:35.24,0:20:36.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你刚刚不是已经
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:36.95,0:20:38.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,打倒了那个叫基纽的家伙吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:39.54,0:20:41.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这次由我来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:41.58,0:20:42.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,随便你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:43.75,0:20:47.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,果然，你不是一般人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:47.88,0:20:49.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,要不是你天生这么恶劣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:49.47,0:20:51.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,本来能成为我的好对手呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:51.97,0:20:55.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你说话还是那么令人心烦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:57.39,0:21:01.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嗯？怎么不变超级赛亚人了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:02.77,0:21:05.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,现在不变也没关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:10.70,0:21:12.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,看来你很自信呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:14.78,0:21:19.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那么，开始我的复仇吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:35.32,0:21:41.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,想当年那一双小手　总难以抱得住的梦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:42.04,0:21:48.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,蓦然间发现　一转身的我们已长大成人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:49.07,0:21:54.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,习习微风拂动街角的步伐　多么想乘上风
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:55.10,0:21:57.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,（新的故事开始）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:58.12,0:22:00.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,来　是时候起程
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:00.77,0:22:02.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,STARRING STAR
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:02.14,0:22:07.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一瞬间铺天盖地点亮　今夜像奇迹一般
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:08.11,0:22:14.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,念念在心间且长此以往　是珍贵无比的温暖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:14.07,0:22:15.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,STARRING STAR
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:15.24,0:22:20.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,哪一天漫天星光倾泻　聚集像珠落玉盘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:20.99,0:22:26.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那么　到时候的星辉　一定会比现在强
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:27.27,0:22:31.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我想是这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:37.32,0:22:38.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嗨！我是悟空！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:39.45,0:22:41.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这力量可真厉害呢，弗利萨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:41.74,0:22:44.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我遇到强敌就会兴奋起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:44.83,0:22:48.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可唯独你是个例外，你总是让我很不爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:49.29,0:22:52.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,让你见识一下，超越神的新力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:53.38,0:22:55.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,下集 『龙珠超』
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:55.47,0:23:00.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,「激斗！弗利萨VS孙悟空 这就是我修炼的成果！」
